e: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">中国心理学会临床与咨询专业委员会正念学组委员，正念研习社创始人，慧商理论提出与建构者</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">曾在Management and Organization Review，Journal of Computational and Mathematical Organization Theory，《管理工程学报》，《系统工程学报》等发表多篇论文</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;">曾先后为<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">交通银行，雅培中国，阿里健康，国药集团、</span></span><span style="font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">混沌大学，杜邦·丹尼斯克，正大天晴、东方航空武汉分公司，华海药业，苏州银行、国家财政部，上海市戒毒管理局、广西财政厅，贵州省贵安新区经济发展局、云南省注册会计师协会，云峰集团、龙工叉车(上海)有限公司、白马广告（上海）有限公司、罗杰斯科技（Rogers），威刚科技(ADATA)等多家机构做过咨询服务。</span></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 6em; margin: auto; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 0px; border-top: 5em solid rgb(222, 217, 138); border-left: 3em solid transparent !important; border-right: 3em solid transparent !important; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 0px; margin: -5em 1em; border-top: 3em solid rgb(255, 255, 255); border-left: 2em solid transparent !important; border-right: 2em solid transparent !important; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 0px; margin: 2em; border-top: 1.5em solid rgb(13, 71, 161); border-left: 1em solid transparent !important; border-right: 1em solid transparent !important; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="margin: -1.6em 0px 1.6em; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">课程目录</p></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; height: auto; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="min-height: 40px; margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【发刊词】1.1我也有像你一样的睡眠问题</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【发刊词】1.2人生转折，我与正念的结缘</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【发刊词】1.3我的正念美睡使命</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【餐前小食】2.1我们的思维是由一个个念头组成的</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【餐前小食】2.2相由心生境由心生一切起于念头</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【餐前小食】2.3我们的决策与行为起于念，执于念</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【餐前小食】2.4因为执念，我们经常把可能性当成事实</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不着的原因】3.1大脑停不下来，想很多与自己相关的事情</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不着的原因】3.2入睡过程感觉被干扰</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不着的原因】3.3习惯的环境被破坏对新环境的不接纳</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不着的原因】3.4担心放不下</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不着的原因】3.5内心有创伤</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不着的原因】3.6睡眠拖延</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不好的原因】4.1大脑一直连轴转，停不下来</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不好的原因】4.2日有所思夜有所梦</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【主食】施治睡不着方法—：断念头学会刹车</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【主食】施治睡不着方法二：接纳</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【主食】施治睡不着方法四：修复受伤的内心</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【主食】施治睡不着方法三：活在当下</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【甜品】下一晚我们如何应对睡不好</p></section></section></section></section></section></td></tr></tbody></table></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; background-image: url('http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appyREsWu1P7491/image/ueditor/55089600_1557043383.jpg?x-oss-process=style/xmorient'); background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-attachment: scroll; padding: 20px 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 80%; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25); border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); padding: 0px 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="t