.6em 0px 1.6em; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">课程目录</p></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; height: auto; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="min-height: 40px; margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【发刊词】1.1我也有像你一样的睡眠问题</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【发刊词】1.2人生转折，我与正念的结缘</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【发刊词】1.3我的正念美睡使命</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【餐前小食】2.1我们的思维是由一个个念头组成的</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【餐前小食】2.2相由心生境由心生一切起于念头</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【餐前小食】2.3我们的决策与行为起于念，执于念</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【餐前小食】2.4因为执念，我们经常把可能性当成事实</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不着的原因】3.1大脑停不下来，想很多与自己相关的事情</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不着的原因】3.2入睡过程感觉被干扰</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不着的原因】3.3习惯的环境被破坏对新环境的不接纳</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不着的原因】3.4担心放不下</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不着的原因】3.5内心有创伤</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不着的原因】3.6睡眠拖延</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不好的原因】4.1大脑一直连轴转，停不下来</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【睡不好的原因】4.2日有所思夜有所梦</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【主食】施治睡不着方法—：断念头学会刹车</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【主食】施治睡不着方法二：接纳</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【主食】施治睡不着方法四：修复受伤的内心</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【主食】施治睡不着方法三：活在当下</p><p style="width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; box-sizing: border-box;">【甜品】下一晚我们如何应对睡不好</p></section></section></section></section></section></td></tr></tbody></table></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; background-image: url('http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appyREsWu1P7491/image/ueditor/55089600_1557043383.jpg?x-oss-process=style/xmorient'); background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; background-attachment: scroll; padding: 20px 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 80%; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25); border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); padding: 0px 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="t